    *   **Hooking `zzafg` (the Iterator)**: If `zzafg` iterates over sensitive data, hooking its `next()` method would reveal the data elements as they are accessed.
        ```javascript
        Java.perform(function() {
            var zzafg = Java.use('com.google.android.libraries.places.internal.zzafg');
