        ```
3.  **Cross-Referencing**: Static analysis tools (like Ghidra or JADX) would be used to find all call sites of `com.google.android.libraries.places.internal.zzafi.zza()`. This would reveal which parts of the application are consuming this `Iterable` and for what purpose, providing context to the iterated data.

